"title": "8026: faith, growth in",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8026: faith, growth in",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Christians are called to have a growing faith, built up by prayer and the encouragement of others, and also through testing.</p>\n<h2>Examples of growing faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:3\">2TH 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:5\">ACT 16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:15\">2CO 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a></p>\n<h2>Weak faith</h2>\n<h3>Weak faith rebuked</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28-Matt6:30\">MAT 6:28–6:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:27-Luke12:28\">LUK 12:27–12:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:26\">MAT 8:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:40\">MRK 4:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:25\">LUK 8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:31\">MAT 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8\">MAT 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:20\">MAT 17:20</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples of weak faith</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:42-John12:43\">JHN 12:42–12:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:38\">JHN 19:38</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:1-Rom14:2\">ROM 14:1–14:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:1-1Cor8:13\">1CO 8:1–8:13</a></p>\n<h2>Strong faith</h2>\n<h3>Strong faith commended and encouraged</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:10\">MAT 8:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20-Matt9:22\">MAT 9:20–9:22</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:25-Mark5:34\">MRK 5:25–5:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43-Luke8:48\">LUK 8:43–8:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:28\">MAT 15:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:29\">MRK 7:29</a></p>\n<h3>The faith of OT leaders</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:3\">1KI 18:3</a> <em>Obadiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs18:5\">2KI 18:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:20\">2CH 31:20</a> <em>Hezekiah</em></p>\n<h3>The faith of Christian leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:12\">1TI 4:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:7\">HEB 13:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts6:5\">ACT 6:5</a> <em>Stephen</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:24\">ACT 11:24</a> <em>Barnabas</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:10\">2TI 3:10</a> <em>Paul</em><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11\">1TI 6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples of strong faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:17-Hab3:18\">HAB 3:17–3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job13:15\">JOB 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:25-Job19:27\">JOB 19:25–19:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:35-Matt14:36\">MAT 14:35–14:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:56\">MRK 6:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:7\">2CO 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:5-Col2:7\">COL 2:5–2:7</a></p>\n<h2>The growth of faith</h2>\n<h3>Praying for more faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:5\">LUK 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:24\">MRK 9:24</a></p>\n<h3>The encouragement of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:7-2Chr32:8\">2CH 32:7–32:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:10\">1TH 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:6-Num14:9\">NUM 14:6–14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:32\">LUK 22:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:11-Rom1:12\">ROM 1:11–1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:2-1Thess3:3\">1TH 3:2–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:20\">JUD 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>Faith strengthened through testing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:18-Rom4:21\">ROM 4:18–4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:5\">GEN 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:2-Jas1:4\">JAS 1:2–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6-1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:6–1:7</a></p>",
